</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">For another way to set one of your own photos as the background,
          right-click on the image file in <span class="app">Files</span> and select <span class="gui">Set
          as Wallpaper</span>, or open the image file in <span class="app">Image Viewer</span>,
          click the menu button in the titlebar and select <span class="gui">Set as
          Wallpaper</span>.</p></div></div></div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">संपूर्ण डेस्कटॉपच्या अवलोकनकरिता <span class="link"><a href="shell-workspaces-switch.html.mr" title="वर्कस्पेसेसमध्ये स्थलांतर करा">रिकाम्या कार्यक्षेत्राचा वापर करा</a></span>.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
</div></div>
